## 部署流程

### 日常更新（推荐）

本地改完代码后：

```bash
# 1. 本地提交并推送
cd /Users/haoren/Downloads/soviet/1
git add .
git commit -m "your message"
git push

# 2. SSH 到服务器拉取最新代码
sshpass -p '020325Guan' ssh root@120.24.20.9 "cd /www/wwwroot/portfolio && git pull origin main"
```

### 一键部署命令

```bash
sshpass -p '020325Guan' ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@120.24.20.9 "cd /www/wwwroot/portfolio && git pull origin main"
```

### 如需重启 Nginx

```bash
sshpass -p '020325Guan' ssh root@120.24.20.9 "/www/server/nginx/sbin/nginx -s reload"
```

## HTTPS 配置

- 证书路径：`/etc/letsencrypt/live/rockorbust.cn/fullchain.pem`
- 私钥路径：`/etc/letsencrypt/live/rockorbust.cn/privkey.pem`
- HTTP 自动 301 跳转 HTTPS
